4y7.editSummary: applied ER's change to the clickbait
4y7.title: C-Class
4y7.clickbait: This page has substantial content, but may not thoroughly cover the topic, may not meet style and prose standards, or may not explain the concept in a way the target audience will reliably understand.
4y7.text:
C-Class pages have substantial content and will often be useful to readers, but they may have significant prose and style problems, may require cleanup, may not cover all significant areas of the topic, or may not explain the concept in a way the target audience will reliably understand.

Contrast:

- [3rk Start-Class] pages, which are sufficiently unfinished that they should be viewed by editors rather than readers.
- [4yd B-Class] pages, which are reasonably comprehensive, have no major stylistic issues, and explain the concept in a way which seems likely to be often enlightening to the target audience.

**[4yg Quality scale]**

* [4ym]
* [4gs]
* [5xq]
* [72]
* [3rk]
* [4y7]
* [4yd]
* [4yf]
* [4yl]
